# Implementation Walkthrough

## Features Implemented

### 1. Appointment Duplicate Phone Logic (Fixed)

**Before:** [findExistingAppointment](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/appointment_service.dart#211-226) checked all dates globally ‚Äî warned on ANY second booking for the same phone, even on different dates.

**After:** Restricted to **same-date only**. Booking the same patient on different dates is now always allowed. Same-date double-booking shows a "Slot Already Booked" dialog with "Keep Old" or "Replace" options.

Files changed:
- [appointment_service.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/appointment_service.dart) ‚Äî [date](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/providers/appointment_provider.dart#193-202) param now **required**
- [create_appointment_screen.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/screens/create_appointment_screen.dart) ‚Äî passes computed date from current selection

---

### 2. Phone Call Button (Implemented)

Added `url_launcher: ^6.3.1` to [pubspec.yaml](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/pubspec.yaml).

In [appointment_list_screen.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/screens/appointment_list_screen.dart), a green phone icon button appears on every appointment card that has a `patientPhone`. Tapping it launches the native phone dialler with the number pre-filled.

---

### 3. Patient Address Split ‚Äî City + Area (Implemented)

**Before:** Single `address` field (City / Area combined text)

**After:** Separate `city` and `area` fields

Files changed:
- [patient_model.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/patients/models/patient_model.dart) ‚Äî added `city` and `area`, kept legacy `address` for backwards-compat
- [appointment_service.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/appointment_service.dart) ‚Äî [createPatient](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/appointment_service.dart#130-171) now accepts `city`/`area`
- [appointment_provider.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/providers/appointment_provider.dart) ‚Äî [createWalkIn](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/providers/appointment_provider.dart#125-192) now accepts `city`/`area`
- [create_appointment_screen.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/screens/create_appointment_screen.dart) ‚Äî replaced single address field with a side-by-side City + Area row
- [patient_info_screen.dart](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/appointments/screens/patient_info_screen.dart) ‚Äî same split in the call-by patient arrival form

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **PocketBase schema change required:** Add `city` (Text) and `area` (Text) fields to the **patients** collection in PocketBase Admin ‚Üí Collections ‚Üí patients ‚Üí Edit.

---

### 4. Clinic Profile ‚Äî New Fields (Implemented)

[ClinicModel](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/models/clinic_model.dart#3-89) now supports:
- `phone`, `address`, `area`, `city`, `state`, `pin`, `location` ‚Äî Text fields
- `logoUrl` ‚Äî built from [logo](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/auth_service.dart#239-244) File field

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **PocketBase schema change required:** Add these fields to the **clinics** collection:
> - `phone` (Text)
> - `address` (Text)
> - `area` (Text)
> - `city` (Text)
> - `state` (Text)
> - `pin` (Text)
> - `location` (Text)
> - [logo](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/core/services/auth_service.dart#239-244) (File, single)

---

### 5. Doctor Profile ‚Äî New Fields (Implemented)

[DoctorModel](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/auth/models/doctor_model.dart#68-191) now supports:
- `phone` ‚Äî Text field
- `dateOfBirth` (stored as `dob`) ‚Äî Text field
- `photoUrl` ‚Äî built from [photo](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/consultations/screens/consultation_screen.dart#860-906) File field

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **PocketBase schema change required:** Add these fields to the **doctors** collection:
> - `phone` (Text)
> - `dob` (Text)
> - [photo](file:///c:/App%20Development/PMS/lib/features/consultations/screens/consultation_screen.dart#860-906) (File, single)

